===Interjection===
'''[[what]] the [[fuck]]!'''

# used to express astonishment (as a shortened form of expressions such as "What the fuck is going on?")
# used to express nonchalance about the consequences of something one is about to do, “I finally said ‘What the fuck?’ and quit my job.”

